SUMMARY:Step 1 - Twilio + Resend Signups (YOU)
DESCRIPTION:Create real accounts and get live API keys.\n\nTwilio: twilio.com/try-twilio\nResend: resend.com\n\nKeys you need:\n- TWILIO_ACCOUNT_SID\n- TWILIO_AUTH_TOKEN\n- TWILIO_PHONE_NUMBER\n- RESEND_API_KEY\n\nNo tool can do this - account creation needs a human.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:autopilot-step2-20260621@autopilot
DTSTAMP:20260620T065400Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260621T092000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260621T093000
SUMMARY:Step 2 - Railway + Vercel Env Vars (YOU)
DESCRIPTION:Paste these 5 vars into Railway:\n- TWILIO_ACCOUNT_SID\n- TWILIO_AUTH_TOKEN\n- TWILIO_PHONE_NUMBER\n- RESEND_API_KEY\n- GROQ_API_KEY\n- DISCORD_WEBHOOK_URL\n\nThen delete old VITE_ versions from Vercel and redeploy.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
