SUMMARY:Step 3 - Claude Code: Stripe Trial Fix (parallel)
DESCRIPTION:Run this while doing Steps 1+2.\n\nPrompt for Claude Code:\n"Add trial_period_days to the Stripe checkout session so new users get a free trial before being charged. Find the checkout session creation in the backend and add the trial period field."\n\nNo need to wait - run it in parallel.
END:VEVENT
