SUMMARY:Step 4 - Smoke Test (tell Claude)
DESCRIPTION:Once Railway has redeployed - tell Claude and the smoke test curls for SMS + email will be run to confirm they actually fire.\n\nDO NOT skip this - it confirms the whole pipeline works end to end.
END:VEVENT
