DESCRIPTION:Run Cowork while Steps 1-4 are happening - no dependency.\n\n- Finish AutoPilot folder organization\n- Build TikTok Day subfolders with scripts\n- McLean's pitch kit folder (demo script + pricing one-pager + notes)
