SUMMARY:Step 6 - Decisions (YOU)
DESCRIPTION:Make these calls whenever:\n\n1. Old empty-reply reviews - re-trigger or leave?\n2. Discord bot - fix or kill?\n3. index.html meta description - skip or include?\n\nNone of these block shipping. Make the calls and move on.
